                    <h2>Mission</h2>
                    <p>
                    University has never been easy and often quite scary. There will be days that seem impossible but at then end of the day you will get though it.
                    But you don't have to face university all by your self, at SZT we are committed to helping university students in providing the support 
                    you need to get through during this challenging time. We want to let university students know that your NOT ALONE. 
                    Our solutions are tailored to meet everyone's needs.
                    </p>
                </article>
             
                <article class="container" id="box3">
                    <h2>Vision</h2>
                    <p>
                    Our hope is end the stigma against mental health, it is something that EVERYONE deals with. We encourge those that are stuggling or know
